{
  "stem": "5375.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I didn't have no time to run to the pile.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was letting it, everything, in my pants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I had no change or whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My body was getting wounded and rotten, you know, from the dirt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But slowly, but slowly, was getting spring, around March, and the sun was getting a little bit warmer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I went, and I opened up the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And somehow-- I went on all my fours, because I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I was so weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I was shivering from my knee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I was walking slowly on my fours to the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I opened up a crack in the door, the sun should shine on me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And slowly by slowly, everyday, it was a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And this friend of mine brought me, still, my dinners and my bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And then, I notice, he fell-- he fell sick, diseased.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But he was lucky, and he died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And outside was a pile with the diseased people, what they were already so diseased that there was no hope for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So they put them outside under the free sky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They gave them the blankets to cover themselves, but the frost was so big.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And there were two friends, it looks like there were two friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And one-- in the morning, I see that he puts his hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Now, I started to walk around already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And slowly, I stole myself out from the diseased barrack, and I went into the healthy one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And it was in the morning, around 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "One puts the hand-- those where they were laying outside under the free sky, covered with the blanket.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "His friend died during the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And he put a hand on his head, and he gave him a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
